0:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/user-day/2025barcelona/the-road-to-devsecops/</guid><description/></item><item><title>User day</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/user-day/2025barcelona/the-security-godfather/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/user-day/2025barcelona/the-security-godfather/</guid><description/></item><item><title>User Day</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/user-day/2025barcelona/cfp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/user-day/2025barcelona/cfp/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="2024-samm-user-day"&gt;2024 SAMM User Day!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The OWASP SAMM team is thrilled to announce its upcoming User Day, as part of &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://lisbon.globalappsec.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Global AppSec Lisbon&lt;svg class="external-link-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"&gt;&lt;path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/&gt;&lt;polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/&gt;&lt;line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;, on Wednesday, June 26th.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The User Day focuses on advancing software security and promoting the use of OWASP SAMM. We invite industry professionals, researchers, and enthusiasts to submit their presentation proposals for this exciting event.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>